tons of coal in six hours 14 times the norm for one shift 
western historians say the feat performed at a donetsk basin 
mine was contrived they say all other work was stopped in 
stakhanovs section of the mine and that a whole gang performed 
auxiliary work that normally had to be done by the man at the coal 
