jolla calif its really of very little significance theres 
really nothing much down there she added referring to the arid 
sparsely populated area where the quake was centered 
just north of the border in calexico calif police cmdr 
torivio flores said some people in the building here felt it 
but it didnt feel like much 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude an earthquake of 5 on the richter scale can cause 
considerable damage in the local area 
