needed 
the ronald reagan presidential foundation wants to build the 
library on a 100acre site which lies partly within a greenbelt 
area that is protected from largescale development by a 
decadeold nonbinding agreement among the communities of 
moorpark simi valley and thousand oaks 
the library scheduled for completion in 1991 would house 
