scheme where was there a beacon of some sanity doumar asked 
was there any did anyone care why didnt anyone care 
some 200 years ago the lord chancellor of england said you 
cannot expect a corporation to have a conscience when it has no 
soul to be damned and no body to be kicked obviously allegheny 
bottling co did not have a conscience 
doumar said he could find no similar case of corporate 
imprisonment to justify his sentence but added stone walls do 
not a prison make 
